text: Alejandro Jordá Candelas (born 19 August 1955) is a Spanish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==Notes== ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Spain Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Barcelona
